snippet: Immigration demonstrations intensified in a southern California town on Friday as protesters filled a desolate road to a U.S. Customs and Border Station to await the arrival of undocumented Central American families for processing....

headline.print_headline: Protesters Gather, Await Arrival of Undocumented Immigrants in California
headline.main: Protesters Gather, Await Arrival of Undocumented Immigrants in California

lead_paragraph: Immigration demonstrations intensified in a southern California town on Friday as protesters filled a desolate road to a U.S. Customs and Border Station to await the arrival of undocumented Central American families for processing.
